## Anti-Patterns (What Failed)

### 1. PixiJS v8 API Changes

**Error:** `Cannot read properties of null (reading 'updateLocalTransform')`

**Why Failed:** PixiJS v8 changed API - components accessed before initialization or after destruction

**Lesson:** ALWAYS check PixiJS v8 API changes - v8 has breaking changes from v7. Never access PixiJS internals without null guards.

---

### 2. React StrictMode Canvas Cleanup

**Error:** Multiple canvas elements created - StrictMode runs effects twice

**Why Failed:** React 18 StrictMode double-invokes effects for development. PixiJS Application created twice but cleanup only removed one.

**Lesson:** React StrictMode in development mode runs useEffect TWICE. Canvas cleanup MUST handle multiple instances. Track canvas refs explicitly.

---

### 3. Blank Screen in Storybook

**Error:** Tela branca no Storybook - no visual output

**Why Failed:** JavaScript error in PixiJS initialization prevented rendering, but no console error visible in Storybook wrapper.

**Lesson:** ALWAYS test in Storybook IFRAME view directly, not in Storybook wrapper. Wrapper hides JavaScript errors.

---

### 4. BlueprintJS CSS Customization

**Error:** Dark mode only changes background and some text colors

**Why Failed:** User explicitly rejected custom CSS approach. AI kept adding custom overrides instead of using native Blueprint styling.

**Lesson:** Do NOT customize component library CSS. Use ONLY native props/classes. Blueprint Intent system, Classes object, Elevation enum - never `var(--custom)` or inline styles for theming.

---

### 5. Hallucinated Blueprint Classes

**Error:** `Classes.FLEX_CONTAINER does not exist in Blueprint.js`

**Why Failed:** AI hallucinated a Blueprint class that doesn't exist. Used training data instead of checking actual API.

**Lesson:** NEVER assume CSS classes exist. Always VERIFY against current docs.

---

### 6. Blueprint Dark Mode Background

**Error:** Dark mode not visually applying - background stayed white/transparent

**Why Failed:** Blueprint.js only styles components, not page body. Used wrong dark color.

**Lesson:** Blueprint ONLY styles its components, NOT body/page. Must add body background manually. Use OFFICIAL colors: light=#f6f7f9, dark=#1c2127.

---

### 7. XState Assumption

**Error:** "@mms/toolkit nao usa xstate"

**Why Failed:** AI assumed XState was used based on training patterns. Actual toolkit uses custom store with immer + useSyncExternalStore.

**Lesson:** NEVER assume state management library. Check package.json dependencies.

---

### 8. Zustand TypedArray Reactivity

**Error:** State mutations not triggering re-renders

**Why Failed:** Zustand with TypedArrays - direct mutation doesn't trigger subscription notifications.

**Lesson:** TypedArrays with Zustand: direct mutation BYPASSES reactivity. Must explicitly call `set()` or trigger version bump after mutations.

---

### 9. AI Duplicate Interface Injection (Gemini)

**Error:** Duplicate interface definition completely breaking the file

**Why Failed:** AI (Gemini) inserted code at wrong location, breaking TypeScript syntax.

**Lesson:** AI can insert code at WRONG LOCATIONS. Always run typecheck immediately after AI edits.

---

### 10. use-gesture Hook Usage

**Error:** `TypeError: gestureBind is not a function`

**Why Failed:** @use-gesture/react hook returns bind function, but implementation used it incorrectly.

**Lesson:** use-gesture returns a BIND FUNCTION, not an object. Spread bind() result on target element.

---

### 11. Tests Passing But App Broken

**Error:** "O site continua quebrando e nenhum teste conectou - tela branca"

**Why Failed:** Unit tests passed but didn't test actual rendering. E2E tests didn't capture console errors.

**Lesson:** Tests passing !== App working. MUST visual verify with Playwright. Check console.error.

---

### 12. RBush in Wrong Phase

**Error:** "RBush e Estrutural, nao Polimento"

**Why Failed:** AI treated performance optimization as polish. RBush is STRUCTURAL requirement for 60k items.

**Lesson:** Spatial indexing (RBush/Flatbush) is STRUCTURAL, not polish. Required for any interaction with large datasets.

---

### 13. Incomplete Architecture Pivot

**Error:** Arquivos Astro ainda existem apos pivot para PixiJS/Vite

**Why Failed:** Architecture pivot was incomplete. Old files not removed, new files not created.

**Lesson:** Architecture pivots must be COMPLETE. Remove ALL old framework files.

---

### 14. Documentation Drift

**Error:** Divergencias entre documentacao e codigo atual

**Why Failed:** Documentation was updated optimistically before code was written.

**Lesson:** Treat documentation as CODE. Verify against reality.

